gnome-activities (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release.
  * Core activity management (create, delete, activate, list).
  * CLI interface with click.
  * D-Bus daemon service.
  * Firefox extension with native messaging support.
  * Systemd user service.

